high_descs: Turn right and move to counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Move to the sink strainer on your left.
Slice up the potato that's sitting in between the glass and the fork.
Turn right and go to the microwave on your left.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Go back to the sink strainer on your left.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn right and go across the room to the fridge on your left.
Open the fridge and place the potato slice on the second shelf in front of and to the left of the apple. Close the door, wait a moment, and take the potato slice out of the fridge.
Go to the microwave on your left.
Put the potato slice in the microwave behind the knife and to the left of the apple.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled slice of potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Move across the room to the counter near the right side of the sink.
Pick up the knife that is on the counter.
Move to the left to the counter that is on the left side of the sink.
Slice the potato that is near the front of the counter.
Turn right and move to the microwave.
Place the knife inside the microwave. Close the door.
Turn left and ,move across the room to the counter on the left side of the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato from the counter.
Turn right and move across the kitchen to the refrigerator.
Place the potato in the fridge to cool.  Take the potato out of the fridge.
Turn left and move to the microwave.
Place the slice of potato inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Use knife to slice potato. Place slice in fridge to cool, followed by placing in the microwave.

high_descs: move to the kitchen sink near the back corner of the room to your right
grab a yellow knife off of the counter to the left of the blue plate
move to the left a bit and face the kitchen sink
slice up the potato on top of the left side of the kitchen sink
turn right and walk to the end of the kitchen counter on your left, turn left to face the microwave
place the knife inside of the microwave
turn left and walk forwards until your reach the sink on your right, turn right to face the sink
grab a slice of potato off of the sink
turn right and walk to the end of the room, turn left to face the fridge
put the potato inside of the fridge, let it cool, then take it back out
turn left and and walk forwards a bit towards the microwave on the right, turn right to face the microwave
place the potato slice inside of the microwave
anns.task_desc: place a cooled slice of potato inside of the microwave
